round of funding comes in?

07:45.310 --> 07:47.360
Look, I know they're not
my biggest fans right now,

07:47.440 --> 07:49.860
but they'll come around.

07:49.940 --> 07:52.860
Did you talk to Braxton
and Wallace?

07:52.950 --> 07:54.030
