07:54.110 --> 07:56.070
What you're cooking
smells divine.

07:56.160 --> 07:57.580
What's it called again?

07:57.660 --> 07:58.910
- Enchiladas.
- Enchiladas.

07:58.990 --> 08:01.870
Rich, what did they say?

08:07.340 --> 08:09.250
I got them to agree

08:09.340 --> 08:12.380
to consider letting you remain
a part of JPL.

08:14.470 --> 08:17.640
