08:17.720 --> 08:20.770
You need to get
a psychiatric evaluation.

08:25.350 --> 08:27.770
<i>I told you so.</i>

08:27.860 --> 08:30.280
There isn't a choice.

08:30.360 --> 08:32.110
You need to regain
peoples' trust.

08:32.190 --> 08:34.320
- Including yours?
- I'm your friend.

08:34.400 --> 08:36.635
- I'm worried for you.
- You're the reason this happened.

08:36.659 --> 08:37.409
That's not fair. The truth

08:37.490 --> 08:38.676
