your innocence.

09:47.310 --> 09:49.190
So, where does that leave us?

09:49.270 --> 09:51.690
Best we could hope for is
parole for good behavior.

09:51.770 --> 09:53.070
How long until that?

09:53.150 --> 09:54.910
Well, less than five years.
Ten, more likely,

09:54.940 --> 09:55.740
