27:09.100 --> 27:11.850
How much, Jack?

27:13.310 --> 27:15.360
How much do you want
for your share of the company?

27:15.440 --> 27:18.400
I have done all I can to protect
you for as long as I can,

27:18.490 --> 27:20.320
but you just don't know
how to quit.

27:20.400 --> 27:21.910
Listen to your friend.

27:21.990 --> 27:24.910
Because we won't do business
with you at the helm.

27:24.990 --> 27:26.410
We'll pull all the orders.

27:26.490 --> 27:28.090
And you'll be left
in charge of a company

27:28.160 --> 27:30.290
with no future and no value.

27:37.170 --> 27:38.920
Ladies and gentlemen,

27:39.010 --> 27:41.090
the new aeon is upon us.

27:41.180 --> 27:44.300
And it is necessary
that we defend freedom,

27:44.390 --> 27:47.010
unless we all wish to be slaves.

27:57.360 --> 27:59.610
Thank you.

27:59.690 --> 28:02.570
Uh, I appreciate
the diligence, Detective,

28:02.660 --> 28:04.280
but the situation's
been resolved.

28:04.370 --> 28:05.846
My daughter and I
have begun to make amends.

28:05.870 --> 28:08.080
Well, that's exactly why
I wanted to call you in.

28:08.160 --> 28:10.410
Is something the matter?
Did something happen to her?

28:10.500 --> 28:12.750
Well, we received
an anonymous package.

28:12.830 --> 28:15.670
Weren't quite sure what
to make of it, but, um...

28:15.750 --> 28:18.590
