the error of my ways.

29:13.560 --> 29:15.480
I swear, Patty. Come home.

29:15.560 --> 29:17.650
It won't ever happen again.

29:21.070 --> 29:24.450
What, you think this is
some kind of proof against me?

29:25.950 --> 29:29.030
