about this harassment.

29:54.640 --> 29:55.640
Let's go, Mabel.

29:55.730 --> 29:58.350
Come on, dear. Come on.

30:07.280 --> 30:09.280
No.

30:13.330 --> 30:15.620
I knew, but...

30:15.700 --> 30:18.540
I didn't want to believe it.

30:19.710 --> 30:23.250
Mrs. Byrne, I'm gonna need
a sworn statement.

30:29.340 --> 30:31.390
Mrs. Byrne, please come with me.

30:33.810 --> 30:37.730
Mr. Byrne, you're under arrest
for the rape of your daughter.

30:39.400 --> 30:42.150
